---
title: Duck Breast with Spring Greens, Spiced Lentils and Apple
description: Are you one of those people who think of duck as a 'dining out' option but would never consider cooking it at home? Well, we're here to change your mind! The crucial thing is to melt the fat so the skin gets crispy. It's called 'rendering' which sounds very technical and cheffy but it's easily done in a frying pan.
